Title: AI Stocks: The Silver Lining in an Otherwise Stormy Tech Market
Summary: Despite recent declines, AI stocks remain a promising long-term investment opportunity. Companies like Nvidia, Palantir, and SoundHound AI have seen significant drops, but the overall AI market is expected to grow rapidly in the coming years, with major tech giants like Meta and Alphabet investing heavily in AI infrastructure.

Title: Front-End Developer Interview Course - Google Amazon Meta Apple Front-End Engineer Mock Interviews 2025 Update
Summary: Interview Kickstart, a leading platform for professional interview prep, has announced its updated Front-End Engineering course for 2025. The course aims to prepare front-end engineers for interviews at top tech companies, covering data structures, algorithms, JavaScript, UI/DOM, and front-end system design.

Title: Top 5 Reasons Students Are Getting Ahead at Iona University
Summary: Iona University is rapidly becoming a top choice for students nationwide, offering innovative academic programs, impressive internships, and a vibrant campus life. The university is focused on preparing students for the future, with an AI-driven curriculum and a strong alumni network providing mentorship and career guidance.
